data.value:
The library serves students, faculty and all Institute employees. The library is located in Building 5 on the third floor. It is an active part of the learning process – an island of learning and quiet. You can borrow books and magazines, get help finding information, photograph and scan materials, study alone or together, and rest in a colorful corner with a fascinating book.
Library opening time: Sun-Thu 08:00-20:00 Fri 08:00-13:00 Library services will continue to be provided remotely to faculty and students
